      "name": "parsley",
      "amount": "1/4 cup",
      "notes": "chopped fresh"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the air fryer to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Season the beef strips with salt, black pepper, and chopped oregano.",
    "Air-fry the beef strips for 5 minutes, or until browned.",
    "Heat the olive oil in the tajine clay vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the tomato paste, beef broth, and browned beef strips to the vessel.",
    "Stir well to combine, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot."
  ],
